h3 Bianbu MCP

p
  | Configure a Bianbu Cloud MCP endpoint for use in Tabby and other AI IDE workflows.

.form-line
  .header
    .title Enable integration
    .description Store connection details in Tabby config
  input(type='checkbox', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.enabled', (ngModelChange)='save()')

.form-line
  .header
    .title Profile name
    .description Display name used for generated config snippets
  input.form-control(type='text', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.name', (ngModelChange)='save()', placeholder='bianbu')

.form-line
  .header
    .title MCP URL
    .description Example: https://your-domain.example.com/mcp
  input.form-control(type='text', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.url', (ngModelChange)='save()', placeholder='https://your-domain.example.com/mcp')

.form-line
  .header
    .title X-API-KEY
    .description Paste the API key copied from the Bianbu Cloud API Key page
  input.form-control(type='password', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.apiKey', (ngModelChange)='save()', placeholder='your-x-api-key')

.form-line
  .header
    .title Request interval (ms)
    .description Recommended stable default: 1000
  input.form-control(type='number', min='0', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.minIntervalMs', (ngModelChange)='save()')

.form-line
  .header
    .title Max retries
    .description Retry count for gateway instability
  input.form-control(type='number', min='0', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.maxRetries', (ngModelChange)='save()')

.form-line
  .header
    .title Retry base delay (ms)
    .description Recommended stable default: 1000
  input.form-control(type='number', min='0', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.retryBaseMs', (ngModelChange)='save()')

.form-line
  .header
    .title Notes
    .description Optional reminder for this endpoint
  textarea.form-control(rows='3', [(ngModel)]='config.store.bianbuMcp.notes', (ngModelChange)='save()', placeholder='Optional notes')

h4(style='margin-top: 1.5em') Copyable MCP snippet
pre(style='white-space: pre-wrap') {{ sampleJson }}

h4(style='margin-top: 1.5em') Bianbu Cloud reminder
ul
  li The MCP URL is usually built as #[code https://&lt;domain&gt;/mcp]
  li The key is copied from the Bianbu Cloud #[code API Key] page
  li If your AI IDE asks for a local #[code command], it probably cannot use remote HTTP MCP directly
